        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersVermin16"/>
        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Improved Grab (Ex):</strong></span> To use this ability, a <a href="ch74s06.html#MonstersVermin15">giant praying mantis</a> must hit with its claws attack. If it wins the ensuing grapple check, it establishes a hold and makes a bite attack as a primary attack (at its full +6 attack bonus).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
