        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersVermin17"/>
        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> A <a href="ch74s06.html#MonstersVermin15">giant praying mantis</a> has a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> checks. *Because of its camouflage, the <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> bonus increases to +12 when a mantis is surrounded by foliage.</p>
